## Step 4 — Install Python without admin (per-user install)

Once you have `python-installer.exe`:

```cmd
python-installer.exe /quiet InstallAllUsers=0 PrependPath=1 Include_test=0
```

Key flags explained:

| Flag | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `InstallAllUsers=0` | Installs for your user only — **no admin needed** |
| `PrependPath=1` | Adds Python to your PATH automatically |
| `Include_test=0` | Skips test suite — smaller install |

